name: 100% Pure Acai Pulp Facial Scrub

The fact that it's water and smudge-resistant makes for a mascara that's sure to keep up during a long work shift or special occasion.

description: Stable, potent Vitamin C boost for all skin types to encourage collagen production, brighten skin tone and to stimulate cellular renewal. Use on clean skin, under other treatments or alone. Use AM and PM. Lightweight, absorbs quickly. For all skin types. For those desiring a brighter, smoother complexion. Directions for Use: Apply a small amount after cleansing, before moisturizing on slightly damp skin. Use morning and night.

description: Application is easy with luxurious, saturated color and a brush that gives a professional finish with no streaking. Easily removed with any nail polish remover. description: Revive your hair and restore bounce and shine to your locks with luscious Aloe and rare Prickly Pear cactus oil. Directions: Apply to wet hair. name: Body Beautiful Shampoo
description: Revive your hair and restore bounce and shine to your locks with luscious Aloe and rare Prickly Pear cactus oil. Directions: Apply to wet hair. name: Brow Duo Pencil
description: This 2 in 1 Brow Duo Pencil glides on effortlessly to fill and define brows, the highlighter brightens to lift the arch creating well shaped natural looking eyebrows. Vegan Friendly. Step 1. Start with clean dry brows, place the pencil along the side of your nose to find where your brows should ideally start and angle the pencil from the outside of your nose to the outer corner of your eye to find where your brows should ideally end. Step 2. Using short dash-like strokes to mimic your natural hairs, softly fill in any sparse areas with a pencil. Step 3. Finally line directly beneath your eyebrows on your brow bone with the highlighter and blend with your finger. This will instantly make your brows appear more defined and arched

name: Charcoal and Biotin Dry Shampoo
description: This unique, scalp-healthy dry shampoo infuses Binchotan charcoal to draw impurities from the scalp and detoxify the scalp and hair. A complex of clay and tapioca & rice starches absorb excess oil at the roots to refresh, clean, and extend the life of your blowout. Witch Hazel extract helps to normalize oil production to prevent an oily scalp, making this dry shampoo a solution oriented product as opposed to just a temporary fix. Super-vitamin, Biotin, provides essential nutrients to the hair follicle to support healthy hair growth.

name: Cleansing Gel
description: This healthy blend of certified organic essential oils and organic castile soap gently cleanses leaving skin refreshed and renewed, never stripped or dry. Made with coconut and jojoba oils, rather than the animal fats and synthetic substances found in many traditional liquid soaps and cleansers, castile soap is hypoallergenic and low impact (with a simple manufacture process that allows for a reduced waste stream and faster biodegradability). Vegan and Gluten free. Travel ready.

name: Coconut Hand Buttercream
description: Our hands are constantly in motion and exposed to the elements, so don't they deserve specially-crafted products to help them feel rejuvenated? Reward their hard work with this rich buttercream that moisturizes, softens, and deeply nourishes with anti-aging vitamins and antioxidants.

name: Contour Shadow Brush
description: The essential makeup brush for enhancing the contours of the lid and crease. Domed bristles fit the natural contour of your crease. Enhance the shape of your eye with a smoky finish or dramatic color.

name: CoQ-10 Toner
description: Hydrate and rebalance your skin's pH level with this Hyaluronic Acid and Aloe Vera based essence. Alcohol-free and formulated with antioxidant CoQ-10 and Sage, this non-drying formula leaves skin primed and protected from pollution and environmental aggressors.

name: Daily Harmony Face Wash
description: This mild face wash helps cleanse away excess oil and impurities without over-drying or irritating skin. In this natural purifying gel cleanser, organic and balancing essential oils of Tea Tree, Geranium, Petitgrain, Peppermint and Eucalyptus penetrate pores to help reduce blemishes and prevent future blemishes, while organic Lavender oil and Aloe Vera Juice help moisturize and soothe skin.

name: Daily Harmony for Oily Skin

Furthermore, most oil-free products marketed for problem skin are filled with toxic chemicals that are simply hazardous and don’t get the job done after all.

name: Defining Mascara
description: Created with rich mineral pigments and certified organic oils, butters and waxes this mascara will instantly add life to your lashes without flaking, smudging or clumping. Though this formula is not 100% organic we made sure that it is 100% natural and effective! Defining Formula - Creamy and rich, this unique formula separates and defines lashes naturally for an overall dramatic eye.

name: Dry Skin Daily Moisture
description: A wonderfully nourishing and moisturizing face serum for dry, mature, and dehydrated skin. Handcrafted from 99% of Certified Organic oils and all natural Vitamin E. Every ingredient is used in a generous proportion to allow for the best, fastest results in nurturing and restoring your skin.

Elixir’s pure plant ingredients are processed without chemicals to produce a superior lip gloss.

name: Empower Eau de Parfum
description: Fresh and spirited. Playful and energizing. An invigorating unisex scent. Men and women can't get enough of it! Top notes: Exquisite citruses from all over the world! Persian lime, Italian Bergamot, Brazilian Orange, Florida grapefruit and lemon for a citrus splash. Middle: Cassis, lemongrass and the peddly soft orange flower play well with the energy and cleaness of spearmint and super grade basil. Base: The sensual warmth of cedar wood, naturally derived benzoin and a drop of Indonesian patchouli make Empower a comforting and traditional eau de parfum.Pour le Monde’s certified 100% natural eau de parfums have impressive staying power. Since these fragrances do not contain any man-made chemical extenders, we suggest using them liberally, don’t be afraid! Naturals work with your own chemistry and gently evolve, so you won’t smell overpowering like synthetics.

Finally, an exclusive blend of natural rice peptides helps to leave the skin feeling hydrated and rejuvenated.

name: Eyebrow Duo

description: Red Flower's Petal Topped Candles fills the room with the intense scent of just-picked flowers using pure flower fragrance. Nature's bloom is transported indoors for 50 hours of breathing, watching, lighting and living. Topped with a cotton wick and scented petals, which can be emptied into a small dish to subtly scent a room. nothing refreshes like the sea that cleanses the earth and leaves it with nothing but new coastal air that brings the smell of flowers, herbs, and trees near the sea. enjoy the smell of this petal topped candle that's mixed with blends of copaiba and clove oils and some eucalyptus. it can make your feel healthier, and more fresh.

name: Organic Rose Soap
description: For sensitive skin. An aromatic blend enriched with our very own organically grown rose petals.

name: Osmia Lip Doctor
description: Osmia's new Lip Doctor is a simple formula with a complicated history. Founder Sarah Villafranco experienced an incredibly frustrating few months with miserable, peeling lips before she figured out she had an allergy to a component of castor oil called ricinoleic acid. She created this formula to soothe her lips, and she has since given it to friends in need, when their lips were in a compromised and unhappy state. It's been so well-received that we decided to make it official!

name: Perfect Zen Body Lotion
description: Indulge your skin with this clean, green, velvety body lotion. Light enough for summer, yet rich enough for winter, our lotion provides deep, soothing hydration all year long. Aroma: A verdant blend of essential oils with traces of sweet orange, bergamot and cedar.

name: Precision Angle Liner Brush
description: Sharply angled and firm bristles make this brush the go-to for a defined line, smoky eye or bold brows. Pairs with powder liners, shadows and brow gels. Made with 100% cruelty-free Taklon synthetic bristles. Duo-color fibers for precision application and blending. Sturdy sleek black handles for a comfortable, stabilizing grip.

name: Pressed Blush
description: ward Winning Lily Lolo Pressed Mineral Blush is available in both matte and shimmer. Lily Lolo pressed blush is the healthy choice for adding a natural flush to your cheeks. Choose from a gorgeous range of pinks, peaches and earthy browns. Silky, creamy texture for a smooth application. Lightweight, color can be built in light layers for a more intense look. Anti-ageing with sea holly extract and argan oil. Moisturizing with jojoba oil. Natural anti-oxidant and anti-bacterial protection. Vegan friendly - Except for Burst Your Bubble & In The Pink. Range of finishes from matt to sheen. Fragrance and talc free. Travel friendly. Oil free. Long-wearing and stays color true all day. Sheer and light, color is built in layers using an angled blush brush

name: Pressed Eyeshadow
description: Alima Pressed Eyeshadows provide bold color payoff in many vivid shades while hydrating and restoring the skin. The silky-smooth powder blends easily for a weightless, long-lasting finish on the lids or as a liner. Vegan and gluten free. Avocado Oil hydrates and moisturizes to increase epidermal elasticity. Jojoba Oil stimulates collagen production. Rice Powder is absorbent, soothing, and rich with vitamins

name: Pure Eyeliner
description: ILIA Pure Eyeliner brings rich, creamy color to the eyes that blends and builds for a day to night look. Packed with the healing oils of Avocado and Castor Seed, they work alongside soothing oils of Coconut to moisturize and protect the delicate area of the eye.

name: Pure Mascara
description: ILIA’s mascaras reference the film noir era. Naturally preserved, Phenoxyethanol free. All Mascaras are made with 100% natural dye. 42% Organic. Vegan.

name: Rosarco Reparative Shampoo
description: Rosarco Repair Shampoo contains a nourishing and reparative blend of rosehip, argan & coconut oils (Rosarco) and vitamin E to combat dryness, restore shine, and strengthen hair from root to tip. This creamy, sulfate-free shampoo removes dirt and buildup without stripping the hair of moisture.

name: Satin Cream Lip Crayon
description: Drench your lips in creamy color that lasts. Packed with healing and organic botanicals, this nourishing formula builds in intensity with each swipe and dances between a satin and a semi-matte finish. Weightless in feel and soothing when applied, it's a lipstick that takes care of your lips. A sharpener is included in the base of the product for a perfect application every time.

name: Satin Matte Eyeliner
description: Richly-pigmented Satin Matte Eyeliner is the perfect complement to mineral eyeshadow. Apply with a damp brush for precise definition or apply dry for a soft, smoky effect.

name: Seriously Soothing Biocellulose Mask
description: Introducing Acure's seriously smoothing biocellulose mask! Truly a change changer for sheet face masks. You won't want to leave home without one in your bag!

name: Shade and Blend Shadow Brush
description: Designed in the iconic ILIA finish, this brush’s soft bristles are made with high-grade, synthetic Taklon, an easy-to-clean, cruelty-free material. Wash brush with mild soap and warm water.

name: Sheer Vivid Tinted Moisturizer
description: A semi-matte formula with soothing botanicals to help calm and revitalize the skin. Aloe Vera aids in long-lasting hydration with White Tea and Rosemary Extract to combat free radicals. Seal in moisture with Sodium Hyaluronate to promote skin microcirculation beneath the surface resulting in a smooth and all-around fuller appearance.

name: Silken Shadow Stick
description: ILIA Silken Shadow Stick glides on effortlessly for a velvety wash of metallic color. Soothing oils of coconut and olive help protect the delicate area of the eye. 100% Natural Dye, 42% Organic, Vegan.

name: Simply Smoothing Conditioner
description: Botanical boost for frizzed, fried, and frustrated hair! An ultra-hydrating combo of marula oil and coconut water that tranforms hair from frizzed and frustrated to smooth and shiny.

name: Simply Smoothing Shampoo
description: Ultra-hydrating with marula oil and coconut water, use on frizzed, fried, frustrated, blown out, straightened, color treated, grumpy and generally worked over hair that takes a daily beating.

name: Skin Dew Coconut Water Cream
description: Skin Dew Coconut Water Cream helps to combat dehydration and promote balanced, moisture-rich, and healthy-looking skin. This powerful, plant-based formula is crafted with: Over 50% pure, mineral rich Coconut Water to hydrate and nourish. Cupuacu Butter, a polyphenol-rich moisturizer sourced from the Amazon, to help neutralize free radicals that contribute to premature aging.

name: Small Fan Brush
description: The Lily Lolo Small Fan Brush is ideal for a soft focus, lightweight application of any of our mineral powders, a sheer application of blusher and bronzer, to soften harsh lines and particularly good for illuminating and highlighting or simply to whip away eye shadow fall out.

name: Smart Start Leave-in Conditioner
description: This lightweight, water-based formula is made with raw lecithin, a powerful, natural extract that fortifies weak strands and prevents future breakage. A duo of rice bran and cumin seed oil guards against heat and UV damage, while bergamot fruit oil softens and detangles, preventing flyaways.

name: Smart Volume Leave-in Conditioner
description: This lightweight, water-based formula is made with raw lecithin, a powerful, natural extract that fortifies weak strands and prevents future breakage. A duo of rice bran and cumin seed oil guards against heat and UV damage, while bergamot fruit oil softens and detangles while preventing flyaways. Flax, a bonus ingredient, adds fullness.

name: Smartcurl Hydrating Conditioner
description: The ultimate hydrating conditioner for every curl type - experience the smoothest hair you've ever had with increased strength, shine, softness and curl formation. Simply dreamy is an understatement.

name: Soap-uccino Soap
description: A wonderful kitchen bar or for the tackle box. Perfect for chefs and fishermen! Is effective at removing annoying odors from hands such as seafood, garlic and onions. Great one-of-a-kind gift that is both practical and useful.

name: Squalane Facial Oil
description: Improve the appearance of texture and tone, skin elasticity and cell turnover with this readily absorbed, 100% pure, Olive derived Squalane. Non-pore clogging, this oil leaves the complexion soft, nourished and never greasy.

name: Sublime Sweet Orange Body Lotion
description: Brighten your day with a boost of refreshing citrus. Sweet orange, cloves, CoQ10 and argan oil leave your skin feeling super soft and extra-energized. 100% VEGAN. Paraben free, sulfate free, phthalate free, mineral oil free, petrolatum free, silicone free and cruelty free.

name: Superfinish Polishing Balm
description: Many stylists call SuperFinish the perfect product. It delivers brilliant shine, de-frizzes and controls flyaways. Plus it moisturizes and protects without being greasy or adding weight - an incredible alternative to oils.

name: Tinted Lip Conditioner
description: Soft, nourishing and boasting natural SPF 15 protection, this sheer, muted mauve will suit most skin tones. ILIA Tinted Lip Conditioner SPF 15 offers natural sun protection and a host of new botanicals. The moisturizing butters of Cocoa and Shea help soften lips and are combined with a rich blend of antioxidant oils of Organic Avocado, Sesame, Cranberry, and Passionflower.

name: Tomato Lycopene SPF 20 Moisturizer
description: Full spectrum SPF 20 protects against the sun's UVA and UVB rays while lycopene, an antioxidant in tomatoes, protects against other environmental damage like smog, pollution, radiation, smoke and other damaging free radicals. Doubles as a silky moisturizer with olive squalane, coconut, and sunflower oils for extra skin comfort and protection.

name: Total Control Styling Creme
description: This uber-versatile botanical formula is ideal for creating virtually any look. TotalControl adds fullness and volume to create gorgeous curls or makes sleek and straight hair when used with a flat iron. This product feels virtually weightless and leaves hair soft, shiny and without frizz. TotalControl will preserve your amazing look for days.

name: True Skin Serum Foundation
description: True Skin Serum Foundation is a complexion-perfecting, serum-infused foundation that’s equal parts skincare and color correction. Weightlessly delivers buildable medium coverage with a silky finish while nourishing with a powerful blend of botanical actives that leaves skin looking like skin. Aloe leaf, rose hip, jojoba and marula oils soothe irritations tame redness, plump fine lines, and ensure the formula effortlessly melts into skin for a more even, luminous appearance. Blurs imperfections and minimizes pores for a complexion that looks refined and refreshed.

name: Ultimate Styling Lotion
description: This 5-In-One botanical formula truly does everything: creates volume, holds style, de-frizzes, adds shine, or defines curls into smooth ringlets. Its an all-in-one amazingly lightweight lotion.

name: Ultra Repair Reconstructing Masque
description: Renew, Replenish, Restore Dry or Compromised Hair. UltraRepair is an intensive treatment for hair that has been compromised by color or bleach processing, heat styling, or environmental factors. Highly effective for smoothing coarse, curly or frizz-prone hair. Leaves hair bouncy, shiny and silky - no matter what its previous condition.

name: Ultrashine Moisture Conditioner
description: EVOLVh's vegan and paraben-free formula is versatile enough to tame a spectrum of hair types, from straight to curly, and fine to super thick. It detangles, adds shine, and is also safe for chemically-treated or colored hair. Active ingredients include wild pansy, sweet clover, and apricot extracts - all of which contain EVOLVh's proprietary phytoblend of nourishing antioxidants - plus amino and fatty acids which restore hair from the inside out, providing anti-aging benefits.

name: Ultrashine Moisture Shampoo
description: Color safe and great for all hair types, this beloved shampoo balances pH levels. EVOLVh's proprietary phytoblend of nourishing antioxidants, plus amino and fatty acids restore hair from the inside out, while providing anti-aging benefits.

name: Velvet Lip Gloss
description: Glam up your gloss game with Velvet, in nine luscious long-wearing shades. Enjoy luxurious texture and shine with maximum moisturizing for ultra-healthy lips. These glosses, firm in the jar, melt at body temperature and glide on easily. Nourishing botanicals like Lemon Balm and Iceland Moss keep lips hydrated and protected from dawn to dusk.

name: Vivacious Volume Conditioner
description: Build dynamic volume with intense lightweight moisture! Limp locks will be a thing of the past, because your hair begin to feel thicker, fuller, and uplifted. Quinoa protein extract supports keratin. Argan Oil + Babassu Oil provide lightweight moisture for root and scalp maintenance. Echinacea Stem Cells promote cellular regeneration at the root level.

name: Winter's Eye Swirl Soap
description: A delicious blend of organic blueberries and herbs. Winter's Eve is a mix of creamy and exfoliating all in one bar. With each use the bar becomes more beautiful. We use real local Fishkill Farms organic blueberries!
